    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Thanks for your reply. We actually pass in a wrapper for a relatively sophisticated cache implementation for instantSearch.connectInfiniteHits where we parse and store the data using custom keys specific to our requirements, passing the same / similar wrapper to responsesCache looks like a reasonable solution for the time being, thanks for the heads up, much appreciated.\r\n\r\nI look forward to refactoring when you guys are done refactoring 😂",
